---
title: Sticky Korean Chicken & Cheesy Corn with Peanut Rice & Asian Radish Slaw
description: Asian cuisine isn’t shy about using big, bold and outrageous flavours. This sticky chicken is no exception - we've taken fried
chicken and teamed it with cheesy corn over nutty rice and a radish slaw for an absolutely vibrant feast.
